<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Members</th>
<td class="" style=""><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chris_Martin" title="Chris Martin">Chris Martin</a><br />
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jonny_Buckland" title="Jonny Buckland">Jonny Buckland</a><br />
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guy_Berryman" title="Guy Berryman">Guy Berryman</a><br />
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Will_Champion" title="Will Champion">Will Champion</a></td>
</tr>
